These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, poppy, lily
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, skydiving
City: paris, london, prague
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, surfing
1. the person who growspoppy is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's sport is baseball##2
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Flower          | marigold      | poppy        | lily     |
| Hobby         | skydiving | rock-climbing | drawing    |
| City   | london   | paris       | prague |
| Sport         | baseball  | climbing      | surfing    |

