.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, emerald, brown
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, thriller
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, siglo, baccarat
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who likes emerald##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
6. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
7. the baccarat-smoker is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Color           | emerald    | brown | red |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | action       | thriller   |
| Pet           | hamster  | guinea-pig   | ferret     |
| Cigar         | siglo | baccarat       | oliveros   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cranberry, watermelon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, family
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, board-games, camping
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, handball, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person eating watermelon is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person eating carrot is between the person watching adventure movies and the person who's sport is rugby##2
5. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is camping is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | carrot | cranberry |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | action | adventure |
| Hobby           | board-games       | baking   | camping    |
| Sport     | rugby      | soccer   | handball |

