.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pumpkin, broccoli
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, engineer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, azalea, daffodil
There are 3 different nationalities: british, italian, pakistani
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
3. the engineer is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the bartender is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the italian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| Food         | pumpkin  | eggplant       | broccoli |
| Job           | engineer     | doctor      | bartender   |
| Flower   | azalea | balloon-flower | daffodil     |
| Nationality   | british      | pakistani   | italian     |

