2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the fan of pop##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
6. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the farmhouse house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Beverage      | water     | juice   | coffee         |
| Color           | ebony | emerald | coral |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | salsa   | pop            |
| House   | art-deco   | farmhouse  | ranch-style         |

