3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the social-worker is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is camping is between the fan of dubstep and the writer##2

