.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster
3 different games are played: monopoly, poker, snooker
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, spanish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, snowboarding, volleyball
1. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing poker is the brazilian##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person playing snooker is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Pet      | hamster     | guinea-pig      | ferret  |
| Game          | poker     | snooker | monopoly       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | spanish    | british      |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton  | snowboarding |

