.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, ambient, pop
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, horror
3 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, horse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, sunflower
1. the person who growssunflower is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the fan of ambient is between the fan of gospel and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | pop       | ambient   | gospel |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror     | disaster |
| Pet           | bird      | chinchilla | horse    |
| Flower         | zinnia  | sunflower     | amaryllis |

