.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, orange, lavender
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, indian, polish
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, trike
1. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
2. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
4. the polish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking water is the person driving the trike##1
6. the indian is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
9. the indian is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Color           | grey | orange   | lavender |
| Nationality   | argentine  | indian    | polish    |
| Beverage         | 7up    | water | milk   |
| Transport     | motorbike  | trike     | airplane  |

