3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the townhouse house and the person who growsiris##2
5. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
6. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
